{"tid":464043,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拉莫斯歡迎尼馬去皇馬","createTime":"2017-11-10T06:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T08:49:26.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"73b549a7ee57e47841ccb811b20eeb9013d1ef64","tid":464043,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T06:18:46.000Z","msg":"尼馬今夏以天價轉會費由巴塞隆拿轉去巴黎聖日耳門，引來外界追訪。<br />\n不過，有新聞指尼馬在PSG生活不愉快，他和教練艾馬利不太合拍，甚至有傳皇馬可能出手挖人。<br />\n<br />\n拉莫斯表示，皇馬絕對歡迎所有人才來投：「皇馬歡迎所有最好的球員前來，尼馬肯定是其中一個。當然，可能他轉去PSG比較容易，要直接由巴塞來皇馬很困難。不過足球世界變化萬千，我絕對歡迎尼馬轉來皇馬，我和他的關係不錯。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=YRk44BQFTIteAawND%2FDYk5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=4d6ed6e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"160266ca5ed6c4ecaa17bb35f851e376c55a1a64","tid":464043,"uid":143284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T06:20:27.000Z","msg":"賤種拉莫斯多嘴狗 -.-&quot;"},{"pid":"240024277f8d3fb5355c08d491ee8d936c9e452e","tid":464043,"uid":90422,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T06:24:40.000Z","msg":"岩啦<br />\n尼馬咁撚賤<br />\n入賤種蝗絕配"},{"pid":"120314e053e705994ce7bfac0d56faafa2747c01","tid":464043,"uid":44523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T06:26:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2fde788bc372599019936895a021250ac5964f63","tid":464043,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T06:27:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>換走監獄馬條辣殺就啱啦</blockquote><br />\n替牙朗"},{"pid":"6cf227016fd9a8d076d3bb55c76b8fe7ad72d866","tid":464043,"uid":106675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:47:57.000Z","msg":"成班笑屁馬過PSG on9,<br />\n人哋擺明過冷河之後去蝗啦"},{"pid":"01f2702afa93eaae1969afa6c55362b294be1181","tid":464043,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:49:26.000Z","msg":"皇馬買簡尼好過泥馬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}